text:
<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Domain Connectivity>
We are investigating connectivity issues for some domains in a single Availability Zone in the US-WEST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Domain Connectivity>
Between 4:50 PM and 6:20 PM PDT we experienced domain connectivity issues in the US-WEST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
